Profiling Models¶

Measurement Paramenters¶

  • Common
    • OMP_NUM_THREADS=12
    • Sigle Process
  • Fugaku
    • A64FX @ 2GHzMKL
    • 1CMG(numactl--cpunodebind=5 --membind=5(12 Core/CMG))
    • PyTorch : v1.4.0 + SSL + DNNL_Aarch64(SSL)
    • Disable LargePage
  • Intel
    • Xeon Platinum 8268 @ 2.9GHz
    • 1Node (numactl--cpunodebind=0 --membind=0(24 Core/node))
    • PyTorch : v1.4.0 + DNNL
    • Disable Hyper Thread
    • HugePage : always
